  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of Celebrex on bone growth into porous
      coated implants, following postoperative total knee arthroplasty administration of Celebrex
      for pain relief.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
