    <intervention_name>Celecoxib</intervention_name>
    <description>Twelve hours prior to their first total knee surgery, patients will need to take an oral dose of Celebrex, 1 pill of 200mg. Following the patient's first total knee surgery, they will continue taking oral doses of Celebrex, 1 pill of 200 mg every twenty-four hours (200mg/day) for a two-week period.</description>
